description: AppSpotr AB develops a application software. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2016-12-19. The firm offers an application development platform, namely AppSpotr, where users can build native applications online. Users can choose their preferred functions, then add the content they like and publish their application on App Store and Google Play. The company mainly serves professionals from small and large companies, advertising agencies and organizations.
name: AppSpotr AB
